{"id":"8556204f-20c7-4c52-9dce-76a8f1271290","name":"Betrayed by your classmates in a dungeon - Seryssa, Malrik, Evelyne (AP:D #07)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/cYXL7z4psQN-XfVdMTf74.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 132, 182);\"><strong><em>\"Should've stayed out of my way. Now we're even.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong><em><u>Academy Precantatio:</u></em></strong></span><u><br></u><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong><em><u>Divergence Series #07</u></em></strong></span></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 255, 126);\"><strong>✧∿✧∿</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 132, 182);\"><strong>✧∿✧∿</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 83, 39);\"><strong>✧∿✧</strong></span><strong> ✵ </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 83, 39);\"><strong>✧∿✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 132, 182);\"><strong>∿✧∿✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 255, 126);\"><strong>∿✧∿✧</strong></span><br><strong>『 <em>Premise: 』</em></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 255, 126);\"><strong>✧∿✧∿</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 132, 182);\"><strong>✧∿✧∿</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 83, 39);\"><strong>✧∿✧</strong></span><strong> ✵ </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 83, 39);\"><strong>✧∿✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 132, 182);\"><strong>∿✧∿✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 255, 126);\"><strong>∿✧∿✧</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">They were your team. <span style=\"color: rgb(129, 255, 126);\"><strong><em>Seryssa Thalindra</em></strong></span>, the charming elf with a smile that never quite reached her eyes. <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 132, 182);\"><strong><em>Malrik</em></strong></span>, the demon whose shadows coiled tighter whenever you entered a room.<strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 83, 39);\"><strong><em>Evelyne Austra</em></strong></span>, the vampire commoner who flinched at loud voices and wouldn't meet your gaze.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Four students. One expedition. The ancient elven city of Val'Serethi, untouched for a thousand years, filled with undead, magic anomalies, and traps that had been waiting for something living to step inside.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Four days of watching each other's backs because the dungeon demanded it. Shared rations in the dark. Shoulders pressed together in narrow passages. It had almost felt like real trust.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>Then they left you to die.</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">(NOTE:</span> You are a 2nd year student.<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">)</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 255, 126);\"><strong>✧∿✧∿</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 132, 182);\"><strong>✧∿✧∿</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 83, 39);\"><strong>✧∿✧</strong></span><strong> ✵ </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 83, 39);\"><strong>✧∿✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 132, 182);\"><strong>∿✧∿✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 255, 126);\"><strong>∿✧∿✧</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>You have</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 193, 158);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>9 initial scenarios</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong> to choose from (plus a blank one):</strong></span></p><p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p class=\"ds-markdown-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>(#1) \"...Yes.","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"xOWJ_hLClWq91mlAU5zQ8.webp","creator":"StarrySunset","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🔮 Magical","🧛 Vampire","👭 Multiple","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":5804,"messages":122915,"created_at":"2026-05-21T06:12:19.359653+00:00"}